<D>__{i don't need to read about it. i can hear about it right now.}
<C>__{matt}
<D>__{scott, let's not talk about that here. it's not the time for that.}
<C>__{scott thorson}
<D>__{all the same to you, i guess. a million here, a million there. just ironic, that's all elizabeth coming into this misfortune just as you're coming into a fortune. she gave you everything, matt. a good, happy home, two beautiful daughters.}
<A>__{matt looks to barry for help, but barry's silence and sheepish look imply he buys into his father's propaganda.}
<C>__{matt}
<D>__{scott, what's your point?}
<C>__{scott thorson}
<D>__{she wanted her own boat. she should have had her own boat, one she would have been familiar with.}
