<A>__{why fight it?}
<C>__{matt}
<D>__{you're right. she deserved more.}
<C>__{sid}
<D>__{for christ's sake, take it easy on the man.}
<A>__{scott turns to sid like he's about to pop him again.}
<C>__{alexandra}
<D>__{my father has been doing a really amazing job under the circumstances.}
